  <description><![CDATA[<p>Santa Margherita is one of the most attractive resorts on the <a data-udi="umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c0a1a2eb5f21493d858ec9013916a8fb}" title="Liguria">Ligurian Riviera</a>. Our hotels are all centrally placed making it an excellent base from which to explore this wonderful region. Trains run up and down the coast linking the resort with the city of Genoa and the beautiful region of <a data-udi="umb://document/bb0a10ac87064cbb81431cb115cd10f9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bb0a10ac87064cbb81431cb115cd10f9}" title="Monterosso, Cinque Terre">Cinque Terre</a>, lying a bit further down the coast.</p>]]></description>
